---
title: Mumbai-Style Haloumi & Veggie Curry with Garlic Rice & Roasted Almonds
description: This deeply rich haloumi curry is like a golden sunset. Filled to the brim with bright veggies and a sprinkling of flair from the
tomato-based sauce, we think this beaming bowl will add the spice you never knew you needed to your night.

